_sText:
This is a breakfloor map based on a space theme. Enjoy! --- OBJECTIVE The object of this map is to break the floor. --- INFO Dig your way to the opposing team and kill them. Use sound as an advantage and be cautious. There is a pit at the bottom so don't go down to deep. Safety beams above the pit. Anti-tker on opposite side of SHOOT. Six block layers. Glass is last layer. Divided into portions. 24 max players --- SECRET Can you find out how to get to the middle? --- BUGS This map is still a beta. Find any bugs? Post it here! --- CREDITS Tstar - Original Breakfloor TDDPred - Space Skybox --- NOTES This map was NOT decompiled. I worked really hard on this map so I hope it shows. Thank you for checking out this map :) Also, you can mess around with the gravity and make it seem like your in space.

Please Assess This Map!
